headline: Engineering and Construction Companies Lay the Groundwork for Growth and Innovation with Oracle Fusion Cloud Applications
summary: Leading engineering and construction companies are turning to Oracle Fusion Cloud Applications Suite to help increase productivity, reduce costs, and enhance the employee and customer experience. With Oracle Fusion Applications, Black & Veatch, Mortenson, Pike Corporation, and WSP Global have been able to standardize finance, HR, supply chain, and customer experience data on an integrated cloud platform, access continuous innovation, and embrace the latest AI innovations to improve efficiency.

headline: Oracle Named a Leader in Gartner® Magic Quadrant™ for Transportation Management Systems for 18th Time
summary: Oracle has been named a Leader in the 2025 Gartner® Magic Quadrant™ for Transportation Management Systems for Oracle Fusion Cloud Transportation Management. This marks the 18th time Oracle has been named a Leader in this report and in this year's edition, Oracle was positioned highest for its Ability to Execute and furthest for its Completeness of Vision. A copy of the report is available here.
